Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.91,0:00:03.77,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:04.65,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.65,0:00:08.81,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! This is why I \Ndidn't want to come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:09.74,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.74,0:00:14.15,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! If you want her to \Nlive, fork over the cash!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.15,0:00:18.58,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Help me! I have a turtle \Nand a hamster who need me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.71,0:00:18.58,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm just a temp. You'll want \Nto talk to the banking manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:21.08,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:27.33,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You're still laughing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:31.59,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. It's not nice \Nto keep laughing at her...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:37.26,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki-chan. That's the kind \Nof thing that hurts most...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:38.60,Main,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:39.54,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:40.64,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:43.39,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Rin! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:46.16,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:47.52,Main,mom,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta take a picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:49.90,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first thing you have \Nto say after all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:54.40,Main,rin,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, are you gonna do your New Year's \NEve broadcast looking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:54.40,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}My stomach hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:56.36,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We're working on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:57.86,Main,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Next. Miyake-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:00:58.41,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:01:03.30,Main,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Some friends of yours heard about this \Nrelay test and came to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.30,0:01:05.49,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:07.42,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.87,0:01:09.67,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Miyake-san, it's been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:12.67,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't heard from you for \Nso long, so we were worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.99,0:01:14.55,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:15.57,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Did it go down?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:18.03,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:19.98,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Ouchies! My leg's cramped!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.98,0:01:22.59,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase, sorry, you take over!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.59,0:01:24.34,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hinata!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.97,0:01:27.98,blackboard,sign,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's Card from Antarctica\NTime Table\NProgram\NIntroduction\NIntroduce the Syowa Base Post Office\N~Japan's most southern post box~ by: Shiraishi Yuzuki\NRecap episode of the girls' Antarctica report by: Shiraishi Yuzuki\NMessages from Japan to the crew\NMessages from family members for Tamaki Mari\NMessages from Hanyu Daisan High School Track Team for Miyake Hinata\NMessages from the National Institute of Polar Research \Nfor the Challenge for Antarctic Crew\NIntroduce life in Antarctica
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:41.16,Show_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2280,1225)}A Place Further Than the Universe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:03.53,Ep_Title,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Bash That Drum Can!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:03.53,Likes/Comments,sign,0000,0000,0000,,12 Likes\N22 Comments
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:03.53,Hashtags,sign,0000,0000,0000,,#Ghosting #Jantei #Satellite Peace #WatchForAnimals
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:12.74,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:41.03,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,That's all the extra stuff we needed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:44.72,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,brought by DROMLAN from Japan \Non its way to the new station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:47.97,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Which means we have everything we need now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:50.63,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we won't be able \Nto create an observatory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.04,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,that can see the stars this year right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.80,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,But a few years from now, if we try for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.87,0:03:57.05,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,We should go, shouldn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:00.47,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's what everyone wants, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.21,0:04:04.89,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Still... that's the place where Takako died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.32,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's not safe at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:09.83,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.82,sign_6044_52_New_Year_s,sign,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.82,sign_6044_53_From_Syowa_Stati,sign,0000,0000,0000,,From Syowa Station
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:14.82,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:18.68,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Mom's spreading it all\Nover social media right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:22.57,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal? It makes better \Nadvertising for the broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:24.76,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:27.20,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... do mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.65,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Your only New Year's \Ncard is to your manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:32.71,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,None for your friends from earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:35.51,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Well... they're New Year's cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:38.31,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,but they won't reach anyone until \Nthe boat gets back to Japan anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:39.38,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna hit the can!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:42.12,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:43.30,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:46.39,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Is she annoyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.04,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Did it hurt that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:50.33,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,She seems a bit stressed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:52.68,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-chan, you're going, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.01,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Piss off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:05.37,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Piss off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.42,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Piss off, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:11.16,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.91,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Piss off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:44.15,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:45.61,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,The weather's cleared up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:48.20,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,so they said they'd bring us along for \Nthe sea ice and geological testing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:51.72,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll prepare the camera, \Nso think about your report!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:53.31,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:54.66,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Expedition! Expedition!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:56.32,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget, you said you'd do the report!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:58.66,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't claim later that \Nyou don't want to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:00.09,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Hinata...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:01.61,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,About before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:04.09,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,That was a test, so it won't cut the mustard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:05.02,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,No—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:07.16,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! They're heading out soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:08.84,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:14.35,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,We did this together three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:18.31,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,Takako-senpai just wanted to do everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:19.76,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,She did?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.76,0:06:22.01,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she went all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:24.25,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,She was here, too, Shirase-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.61,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:28.47,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.62,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:35.96,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:39.38,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,It's all ice up ahead, so we're \Ndigging a hole with steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:43.39,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I think we went to Rundvågshetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.55,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a powerful name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:49.14,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,It's a place with exposed rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:53.07,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask Nobue-san, \Nshe might take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:53.68,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:58.19,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Ice here! Nobue-san at geology? \NDo you read? Over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:02.46,Italics,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't heard from him since Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:05.47,Italics,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,The garnet he gave me two years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:08.99,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Dry rocks and dry love...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:12.47,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,No email. No nothing from Yu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:16.62,Italics,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,She's currently unable to talk. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:24.60,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:27.38,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously. The difference in \Nair temperature is extreme...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:31.06,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.84,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.95,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,So cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:36.48,sign_10910_114_Watch_for_animal,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,100)}Watch for animals
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:47.68,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Antarctica really is amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:50.44,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's neat to see it from this angle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:57.12,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,The sky is flowing by!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:59.90,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll see an aurora?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:01.30,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,At night, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:03.63,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,But it won't become night
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.87,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,during the time we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:08.58,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:13.86,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Is something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:15.39,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Bothering me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:19.15,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my lips get so \Nchapped with the dry air,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:21.14,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,but my lip balm is frozen,\Nso it's hard to put on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:22.66,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:25.25,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It really is hard! \NIt's like your skin is peeling off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:26.51,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:27.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:30.15,sign_12172_130_Take_Care_Outsid,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Be Careful Going Outside
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:30.44,Italics,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,All crew outdoors, please seek\Nshelter in the main building
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:33.16,Italics,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,or a building with emergency rations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.37,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's not getting better at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.04,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You should probably give up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.87,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd Shirase go, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:44.55,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Someone asked her earlier if \Nshe knew how to play Mahjong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:46.45,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,For real? Can she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:49.55,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It sounded fun, so I looked \Nover her shoulder, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:54.53,Flashback,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how do you read the one that \Nlooks like a person next to a five?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:55.35,Flashback,shira,0000,0000,0000,,"Go."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:57.87,Flashback,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you've got some white ones \Nmixed up in your reserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:08:59.64,Flashback,shira,0000,0000,0000,,They're not reserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:02.39,Flashback,kima,0000,0000,0000,,That bird is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.14,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,"Get out!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:05.32,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,...she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:06.62,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,That's rather cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:09.46,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Right? I was only asking questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:12.46,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase's always been testy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.36,sign_13220_149_Block_List_Misat,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Block List\NMisato   Edit\NAyaka    Edit\NSatsuki    Edit
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.36,sign_13220_150_Delete_Block_and,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Delete\N{\c&H9D927A&}Block and Delete
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:13.36,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:17.07,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:21.06,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Menhon, Double South, \NThree Dora nets me 16,000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.58,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,Are you for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:27.06,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you been playing with \NTakako since you were little?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:28.27,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, once in a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.86,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Let's quit. We can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:33.09,sign_13683_159_Missing_Line_,,0000,0000,0000,,Jantei
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:33.09,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Not against the daughter of Gin and Takako...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:35.37,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Is Miyake-san here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.67,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:37.82,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:41.43,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,We got an email from her \Nfriends addressed to the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:43.69,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:44.69,sign_13995_165_National_Antarct,sign,0000,0000,0000,,National Antarctic Research Center\NRe: About the broadcast timetable
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:44.69,sign_13995_166_National_Antarct,sign,0000,0000,0000,,National Antarctic Research Center\N(To Miyake Hinata) Hanyu Daisan High School Track Team\N\NNational Antarctic Research Center\NRe: About the broadcast timetable
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:47.27,sign_14019_167_Declare_all_acco,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Declare all accounts online\NDeclare all accounts offline\NGet new mail\NLink accounts\NEmpty the trash can\NEmpty the spam folder\NNew mailbox\NNew smart mailbox
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:47.94,sign_13995_165_National_Antarct,sign,0000,0000,0000,,National Antarctic Research Center\NRe: About the broadcast timetable
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:47.94,sign_13995_166_National_Antarct,sign,0000,0000,0000,,National Antarctic Research Center\N(To Miyake Hinata) Hanyu Daisan High School Track Team\N\NNational Antarctic Research Center\NRe: About the broadcast timetable
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:50.57,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,None to the base, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.07,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd write me every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:02.81,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Want to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:03.92,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:09.09,sign_14019_167_Declare_all_acco,sign,0000,0000,0000,,National Antarctic Research Center\N(To Miyake Hinata) Hanyu Daisan High School Track Team
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.34,sign_13995_165_National_Antarct,sign,0000,0000,0000,,National Antarctic Research Center\NRe: About the broadcast timetable
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.34,sign_13995_166_National_Antarct,sign,0000,0000,0000,,National Antarctic Research Center\N(To Miyake Hinata) Hanyu Daisan High School Track Team\N\NNational Antarctic Research Center\NRe: About the broadcast timetable
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.82,sign_15091_177_you_quit_the_tra,sign,0000,0000,0000,,you quit the track team and\Nquit school so suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:32.15,sign_15091_177_you_quit_the_tra,sign,0000,0000,0000,,We wish we'd said something to the older girls. \NWe're sorry for leaving you all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:34.02,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.43,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:37.07,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:39.28,sign_13995_165_National_Antarct,,0000,0000,0000,,National Antarctic Research Center\N(To Miyake Hinata)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.75,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:43.50,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:46.54,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,But that was addressed to Hinata-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.50,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:52.50,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But... but I was worried, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:55.51,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed so mad about something, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:58.26,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,you wouldn't say anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.61,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You were mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:01.01,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What, you saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.53,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You should have said something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:03.98,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:06.27,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were hiding something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:09.27,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Something you weren't telling us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:14.03,sign_15091_177_you_quit_the_tra,sign,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry for leaving you all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:28.95,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you in advance, \Nit's a totally gross story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:32.55,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to talk about it, \Nand I hate that you asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:33.71,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:41.18,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,In short, it's about why \NI stopped going to club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:46.64,Flashback,club,0000,0000,0000,,It's the competition, \Nso the fastest people should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:48.97,Flashback,club,0000,0000,0000,,Your year and stuff doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:52.04,Flashback,hina,0000,0000,0000,,But for the third-years, \Nthis will be their last competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:54.79,Flashback,club,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly! It would be more \Nrude to go easy on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:59.32,Flashback,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Two hundred meter, Miyake Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.17,Flashback,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:08.88,Flashback,sen,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say something to that idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:12.07,Flashback,club,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course... we told\Nher to be more sensitive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:17.33,Main,hin,0000,0000,0000,,In that instant, nothing mattered to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:24.25,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But it does matter! \NThey're the ones to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:27.62,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Humans can be scary, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:35.02,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,After I quit, they kept spreading all \Nkinds of rumors to lay the blame on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:39.07,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you quit school?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:41.48,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:45.74,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:49.11,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Then the ones who sent the email are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:51.61,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. My old teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.20,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,They want to talk during the broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:58.00,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,They said they were proud their \Nfriend went to Antarctica.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:01.88,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Though mainly, I was thinking \N"Oh, were we friends?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:10.57,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.96,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,What? Different from what you imagined?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:19.01,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost otherworldly, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:20.68,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:22.44,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What an unusual color!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:25.05,Main,yume,0000,0000,0000,,We'll set up a tent and \Nantenna down that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.27,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:28.75,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:32.70,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna \Ndrag this out? Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:35.02,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like being treated this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:35.93,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:38.71,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Look, why do you think I came to Antarctica?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:41.21,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Because there's nothing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:46.21,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to go to an empty place \Nwith no one to tie me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:48.22,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Look, isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:52.47,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Glaciers! Strata! Water from melted snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:56.36,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Colors and shapes I've never seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:59.10,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,We're in a place isolated \Nfrom everything we know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:02.98,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,a completely different world \Nfrom where we've been before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.23,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I came here to enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.83,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't mean anything\Nif you're all sad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:12.61,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. Then we'll forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.38,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,First, we've got camping to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:16.24,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:17.67,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.37,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It does mean something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:23.04,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It absolutely does mean something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:34.44,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a sci-fi movie, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:37.03,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Want to drink the water? It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:38.18,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We can drink it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:41.77,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,In a way, it's the cleanest \Nwater on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:44.04,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Hardly anyone's ever touched it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:46.94,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,and it doesn't get warm \Nenough to breed bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:48.58,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:49.19,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:55.08,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:56.49,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:14:59.00,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.95,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! It's delicious and cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:05.50,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It really hits the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:08.05,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Want some, Shirase-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.33,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:11.84,Main,yuma,0000,0000,0000,,We got through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:13.98,Main,yuma,0000,0000,0000,,Talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.72,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:22.18,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... this is Kobuchizawa at Rundvågshetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:23.13,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:26.35,Italics,kana,0000,0000,0000,,This is Syowa. We read you loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:28.89,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,How is the scenery? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:33.13,Italics,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Um... It's like we're surrounded by cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:34.05,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:36.36,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Takako said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:39.30,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,The minute we got there,\N"I want to eat chocolate cake!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.28,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,My mother said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.40,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's the best natural water I've ever had!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:54.39,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:55.00,Main,yume,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:57.98,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari-san, you're good \Nat the strangest things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:15:59.26,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,That's not strange, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:02.26,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Can they see this on the satellites?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:06.81,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We use these so they can check \Nour location on the satellites.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:09.14,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,It will definitely show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:11.03,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not taking it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:13.15,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:17.24,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:17.24,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:19.90,Main,yume,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it bother you. \NShe does this constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:26.61,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,We even put a plate here. \NSomeone's watching, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.04,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing personal, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:44.55,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:47.00,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Especially since it's getting colder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:49.06,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,And now it's time for...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.44,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:53.32,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Next time we get hot water \Ngoing, let's make tamagoyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:55.44,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You really like tamagoyaki, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:59.06,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,She did eat a lot of it for \Nbreakfast in Singapore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.30,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:03.71,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to collect water. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:07.13,Main,ima,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough? \NSorry I used it all earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.01,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:17.17,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's freezing when the wind blows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.27,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I could just die right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:25.36,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about what \NI'd do in your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:31.44,sign_15091_177_you_quit_the_tra,sign,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry for leaving you all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:28.59,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,If someone had treated me so awfully,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:31.44,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,then called me up out of the blue, \Nas though nothing happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:35.25,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,wanting to apologize for the \Npermanent damage they'd done...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:36.88,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.82,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't be okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.33,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:44.07,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You're not me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:46.55,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:48.58,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:51.34,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:53.33,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Take off your gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:55.09,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hand them over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:02.59,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Your hands are enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:06.15,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase, you're so annoying, \Nthe way you keep talking and talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:09.37,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:14.45,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I guess I'm still scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.29,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:17.68,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:20.86,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But we...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.69,0:18:24.99,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I said your hands were enough, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:34.68,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for bringing me along.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:38.88,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Tamagoyaki's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:41.54,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We're on our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:44.79,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:52.02,sign_27106_329_12_31_Choose__Ne,sign,0000,0000,0000,,12/31\NChoose Your Own New Year's Soba\NTempura\NMochi\NPlain
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.78,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,You suck! They're not supposed\Nto be flat noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:55.03,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,They're thin enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:55.92,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Start from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:57.03,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:18:59.83,Italics,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to roll in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:00.91,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:03.24,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,My sun tan never recovered...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.28,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's proof that you're \Nenjoying Antarctica.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:06.97,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:11.78,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'll feel \Nbetter if I forgive them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:13.82,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You want to forgive them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:16.74,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,If it would make me feel better, I might.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:22.12,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,But when I imagine them looking all relieved \Nafterwords, it gets under my skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:24.76,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,"Piss off"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:27.38,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:30.30,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pretty petty person, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:36.62,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's 9:00 AM here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:38.74,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,A six-hour difference from Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:41.03,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Before we start, may I say one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:45.72,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:49.80,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I beg your pardon, but could \Nyou leave Miyake Hinata alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:50.95,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:56.23,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You might think Hinata has been holding a \Ngrudge against you since she quit school,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:59.83,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,that she's been suffering badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.88,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you think she spends every day crying,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:05.03,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,thinking about what happened to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:06.85,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.65,0:20:08.49,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:14.09,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:19.17,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata-chan is having a super, \Namazing fun time with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:23.19,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,She's having a really fulfilling trip \Nof the sort you can't get where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.19,0:20:23.86,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:27.02,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata is already looking forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:29.27,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,She's already walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:31.51,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,She's taking her steps with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:32.02,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:35.13,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! It's friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:39.04,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike Hinata, I'm a real jerk, \Nso I'll say it outright.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:42.50,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You can't live your lives in \Nthis halfway state forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.37,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You hurt someone and made them suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:47.26,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Now you get to live with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:50.14,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you get for hurting someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:53.10,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you get for hurting my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:58.53,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:06.55,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can come crawling back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.00,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Piss off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.41,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get things ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:20.22,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:28.96,Italics,vo,0000,0000,0000,,The year is nearing its end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:31.53,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:33.64,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,Last year's video, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:35.71,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:40.73,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-kun! Yu-kun! Yu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:42.29,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:43.45,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Casting away our worldly desires!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:44.48,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:46.60,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,...like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:48.73,Main,ima,0000,0000,0000,,Let's bash the bad thoughts \Naway, Hinata-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:50.98,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What if we break it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:53.49,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,So what if you do? It's just a drum can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:56.37,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Good point!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:58.85,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do the first one together!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:02.50,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:36.52,sign_33879_393_A_Place_Further_,hina,0000,0000,0000,,A Place Further\NThan the Universe
